Class BukkitSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.taylorkelly.mywarp.bukkit.settings.BukkitSettings
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    me.taylorkelly.mywarp.platform.Settings

    public class BukkitSettings
extends java.lang.Object
implements me.taylorkelly.mywarp.platform.Settings
    The settings when running on Bukkit. This implementation relies on Bukkit's configuration API to manage the actual configuration file.
